title: ISic000413. I.Sicily inscription 000413
body:
1[--- vi]r primario VI味I味[---]

1[---..]RPRIMARIOV..[---]

Facsimile Images

Apparatus criticus

  • Text of CIL;
  • line.1: Manganaro 1989: [- ex test(amento)? -].ceri Mari qui.[q(uennalis)].

translation

commentary

Without more detailed autopsy, clarification of the reading remains difficult, but there is little basis to read Q instead of P, as proposed by Manganaro.
